# CBT-I personal-data workbooks — NEVER commit. Both repos are public; these
# contain dated sleep, alcohol-unit counts, and free-text comments. The import
# script takes the path as an argument and reads from outside the tree; this
# rule is defence-in-depth against an accidental in-tree copy + `git add -A`.
cbti_user_data_*.xlsx
cbti_assessment_data_*.xlsx

